title: Honey Pot
itunes:title: Honey Pot
description:
PANTS with Kate Moennig and Leisha Hailey

Produced by Melisa D. Monts and Diamond MPrint Productions

Edited by Diane Kang 

 

Leisha wants Kate to sing on the podcast. Kate wants a LASIK date in the near-sighted future. Kim Dickens joins for a bit. Then they discuss Leisha’s attempt at redecorating their set office and Kate’s unsupportive commentary from the sidelines. #BankAesthetic 

 

Follow us on Twitter @ThePantsPod

Follow us on Instagram @ThePantsPod

Email us: kateandleisha@gmail.com

Music: Carol Parra @csssuxxx
